 best work late over this trip here just over 3 weeks ago when finishing runner-up. Michael McNab replacing an apprentice is a strong lead, and she is the main danger to the top pick. 6. PUROSANGUE tried hard when finishing fifth on debut at Te Aroha 18 days ago, and he will be better for that experience. He has won a trial prior, and he will be spot on for this assignment on his home track. Stick with him for all top 4 combos. 2. COWBOY only peaked late when finishing fourth fresh at Pukekohe 2 weeks ago. He has the winkers on for the first time, and he can figure in the top 4 again. 5. BOLD AND BRAVE finished fifth in the same race as the fourth pick when making his debut. Include.\",\"runners\":[1,9,6,2,5],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,6,14]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,3,14]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,7,6]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,14,8,7]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,1,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,7]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MAT","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNum